column3: Text
Hey! I've lost someone. Can you help me find him?
Who?
I don't remember his name.
Is there anything you do remember?
I think he was wearing a teddy bearsuit or something...
How are you doing?
Good.
I have something I wanted to tell you.
I don't know what it means anymore, but perhaps you do.
I think it was something like "Wake up. You're dreaming."
Oh?
No... That can't be right.  Maybe it was "Wake up.  This is a dream?"
What's the difference between those two?
"Wake up.  This is a nightmare."  Yes. that's it.
Okay?
Wake up. The sky is weeping
Wake up. The blind are following the blind.
Wake up. You cannot stay here forever.
The sky is so pink today.
